---
title: "Gridcoin - Blog"
description: "This blog is for official announcements and important community updates."
---

<section  style="padding-bottom:15px; padding-top:100px;">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="hidden-xs col-sm-4 col-md-4 col-lg-4" style="text-align:center;">
                <img src="/assets/img/LOGO/GRCLogoOnly_Purple_White_Solid.png" alt="GRC"  style="width: 200px;" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-8 col-md-8 col-lg-8" style="margin-bottom:5px;">
                <h3 style="text-align: center;">Welcome to the official Gridcoin blog!</h3>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    We'll be posting Gridcoin and BOINC related announcements to this blog so as to improve communication across the entire community.
                </p>
                <p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    If you wish to publish a blog post, please either submit an <a href="https://github.com/gridcoin-community/Gridcoin-Site/issues/">issue</a> or a pull request on the <a href="https://github.com/gridcoin-community/Gridcoin-Site/pulls">Gridcoin website GitHub repo</a>, including your blog post in the <a href="https://github.com/gridcoin-community/Gridcoin-Site/blob/master/data/blog.yml">blog data file</a>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section  style="padding-bottom: 50px;">
    <!-- BOINC Content -->
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <% data.blog.posts.each do |post| %>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12">
                    <h4><%= post.title %></h4>
                    <p><%= post.content %></p>
                    <a href="<%= post.link_primary_url %>"><%= post.link_primary_text %></a>
                    <a href="<%= post.link_secondary_url %>"><%= post.link_secondary_text %></a>
                    <hr/>
                </div>
            <% end %>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>